### Arabic

وَقَالُوا۟ نَحْنُ أَكْثَرُ أَمْوَٰلًا وَأَوْلَـٰدًا وَمَا نَحْنُ بِمُعَذَّبِينَ

### English

Adding, “We are far superior ˹to the believers˺ in wealth and children, and we will never be punished.”